# Styles (SCSS)

## Module System

**Dart Sass with `@use`/`@forward`** ŌĆö NOT `@import`.

```scss
// Component SCSS
@charset 'UTF-8';
@use 'abstracts' as *;

.cmp-component { /* ... */ }
```

```scss
// abstracts.scss ŌĆö @forward all shared modules
@forward 'abstracts/breakpoints';
@forward 'abstracts/colours';
@forward 'mixins/mediaqueries';
@forward 'mixins/typography';
```

## Naming

- Component styles target AEM Core Component classes: `.cmp-{name}__*`
- Wrapper modifier classes: `.project-{name}--{variant}`
- Design tokens via CSS custom properties: `var(--project-color-*)`, `var(--project-spacing-*)`

## Rules

- Use `@use 'abstracts' as *` ŌĆö never `@import`
- Use existing shared mixins for breakpoints, typography, focus states
- Use CSS custom properties for design tokens ŌĆö don't hardcode colours or spacing
- New component styles co-locate with component JS
- Use the shared focus mixin for consistent focus indicators

## Build System

- **Primary Build Tool**: `@netcentric/fe-build`
- **CSS Processing**: PostCSS with SCSS support
- **Linting**: Stylelint with SCSS plugin

## BEM Methodology

```scss
.{prefix}-button {
  &__label { }    // Element
  &--primary { }  // Modifier
  &--is-loading { }  // State
}
```

## CSS Variables

```scss
.{prefix}-component {
  --{prefix}-component-color: #333;
  --{prefix}-component-background: #fff;

  &--primary {
    --{prefix}-component-color: #fff;
    --{prefix}-component-background: #007bff;
  }

  &__content {
    color: var(--{prefix}-component-color);
    background-color: var(--{prefix}-component-background);
  }
}
```

## AEM Style System Integration

```scss
// CORRECT: Modifier at root, descendant selectors for elements
.{prefix}-component--variation {
  .{prefix}-component {
    &__element { ... }
  }
}

// WRONG: Hybrid Block-Modifier__Element pattern
.{prefix}-component--variation {
  &__element { ... }  // Creates .{prefix}-component--variation__element ŌĆö WRONG
}
```

## Stylelint Rules

- **`max-nesting-depth`**: 8 levels maximum
- **`media-feature-range-notation`**: Use prefix notation
- **Font size units**: Only `rem`, `px`, `em` allowed

## Focus Management

Always use the shared focus mixin from `commons/sass/mixins/_focus.scss`:

```scss
@use 'abstracts' as *;
.{prefix}-button { @include focus; }
```

- Never use `outline: none` on `:focus` without `:focus-visible` replacement
- Never hardcode hex values for focus colors ŌĆö use CSS variables

## Market-Specific Styles

- **Never use `html[lang]` selectors** ŌĆö they are fragile
- Create `_{component}-{brand}-{market}.scss` partials for market overrides
- Add `@use` to the brand's main `*.clientlibs.scss` entry file
